text: Mohamed Hussein (born 10 September 1991) is an Egyptian swimmer. At the 2016 Summer Olympics he competed in the Men's 200 m individual medley. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic swimmers of Egypt Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:African Games bronze medalists for Egypt Category:African Games medalists in swimming Category:Competitors at the 2011 All-Africa Games Category:Male medley swimmers Category:Male backstroke swimmers
